Copy all subjects from the two archive diskette to a hard disk.  The subjects are

  GRiDLink
  Incs
  Libs
  OsIncs

Select the following develop file

  "z GRiDLink & Phonlink~Develop~"

Press CODE-G and select Yes for only the following source groups

  Vfs,Vipc,Misc sources (common to all)
  Sources common to all GRiDLinks
  GRiD-Os GRiDLink sources
  Sources common to all PhoneLinks
  GRiD-Os PhoneLink sources
 
Select Compile & Link

  Select All Plm Sources for all files with .Plm
  Select All Asm Sources for all files with .Asm
  Select Yes for all files with .Pas

For Link select yes for 

  Vfs/Vipc/Misc
  GRiD-OS GRiDlink
  GRiD-OS Phonelink

Compilers PLM    Version 2.3
          Pascal Version 3.0
          Link   Version 2.0

NOTE:  While linking there are several places where it will be ask for confirm to continue.  Keep confirming.

The final run files will be under the subject obj with the following names:

  @GRiDLink~Device~
  @Phonelink~Device~


